Package: runCERIS
Title: Critical Environmental Regressor through Informed Search
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Yu-Ru", "Chen", email = "yuruchen@iastate.edu",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: Identifies critical environmental windows and covariates driving
    genotype-by-environment interaction in multi-environment trials. Includes
    the CERIS exhaustive search algorithm, Joint Regression Analysis (JRA),
    Joint Genomic Regression Analysis (JGRA), cross-validation methods, and
    genomic prediction. Provides a Shiny application for interactive analysis.
